Security-Suite 1.4.0

	* [Security] Disable the SecurityLog entirely, (SytemLog now handles all of that).
	* [Performance] Switching from ::Construct to __construct saves memory and boosts performance on
	  extremely heavy pages.
	* [Feature] WP-emulation honeypots should not be exposed to crawlers and site indexes.
	* [Feature] Add support for a simple site password, similar to an .htpasswd.
	* Ensure that the HTTP simple password option only applies to WEB mode.
	-- Charlie Powell <charlie@eval.bz>  Sat, 22 Mar 2014 15:02:56 -0400

